{"article_id":"AIE6q4grdQcmB1Ck","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Share All sharing options for :","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"The 7 most disturbing allegations about Trump in John Bolton ' s forthcoming book","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"John Bolton is publishing a book","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that recounts his tenure as President Donald Trump ' s national security adviser .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"The Trump administration on Tuesday sued","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to delay its release ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"a week before it was set to be published .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"So , naturally , major news outlets have now \" obtained \" the book","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and are releasing the most explosive passages from the memoir .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Bolton ' s book , The Room","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Where It Happened ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"contains numerous remarkable allegations about things","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"President Trump said and did during his interactions with foreign leaders","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"- none of which ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"it ' s worth remembering ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Bolton felt compelled to speak publicly about in the months","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"since he left the administration","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"or to testify about","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"unless he was formally subpoenaed during the Senate ' s impeachment trial .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"now that he has a book to sell ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"the longtime Republican foreign policy hand seems ready to dish .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"In the book , Bolton","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"- who , again , declined to voluntarily testify under oath during the impeachment trial","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"because the White House told him not to -","depth":13},{"id":25,"text":"accuses the Democrat-led House of Representatives of committing \" impeachment malpractice \"","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"by not going beyond Trump ' s dealings with Ukraine","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"to investigate other disturbing actions of Trump ' s .","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"Like , for example , Bolton ' s claim","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"that Trump asked Chinese President Xi Jinping for electoral help and other instances","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"where Trump sought to use his power for personal or political gain .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"( hasn ' t seen the book in its entirety ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"so we are relying on reports and excerpts","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"published elsewhere . )","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"As national security adviser , Bolton was definitely in the room","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"where stuff happened ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"and as such was privy to Trump ' s conversations with world leaders , maybe more than most .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Which lends some degree of credibility to his claims .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"At the same time ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"this is Bolton ' s account ,","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"and it ' s not like he and Trump parted on great terms .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"Bolton , a conservative hawk , didn ' t always seem like the right fit for Trump ' s more isolationist foreign policy approach ,","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"and the two clashed over issues like North Korea and not being able to start wars .","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"So some of Bolton ' s claims may be self-serving or tough to verify .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Of course , verifying his claims might have been easier","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"had Bolton testified before Congress under threat of perjury .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Acknowledging","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that there are no heroes here ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"below are some of the wildest and most disturbing tidbits from Bolton ' s memoir .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Read them ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and imagine an alternate universe","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"where Bolton ' s mustache is moving up and down","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"as he delivers an opening statement before the House Intelligence Committee in the fall of 2019 .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"It kind of helps .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"According to Bolton ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"President Trump brought up his reelection prospects with Chinese President Xi Jinping during a one-on-one meeting on the sidelines of the Group of 20 summit in Japan .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Xi mentioned China ' s critics in the US ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"according to Bolton ,","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"Trump thought","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"the Chinese leader meant Democrats .","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"So Trump apparently thought","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"he had an opportunity .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"\" He then , stunningly , turned the conversation to the coming U.S. presidential election ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"alluding to China ' s economic capability","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"to affect the ongoing campaigns ,","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"pleading with Xi","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"to ensure","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"he ' d win , \"","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"Bolton writes .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"\" He stressed the importance of farmers ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"and increased Chinese purchases of soybeans and wheat in the electoral outcome .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"I would print Trump ' s exact words","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"but the government ' s prepublication review process has decided otherwise . \"","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"Of course , Trump had already publicly asked China to investigate his political rivals","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"back when he was already being investigated for pressuring Ukraine to do the same ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"so it ' s not actually as bad as the other thing","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"that allegedly happened in this meeting .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Trump told Xi to go ahead with the internment of Muslims in China","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"According to the Washington Post ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Bolton writes","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"that at the same meeting between Trump and Xi at the G20 , the Chinese leader defended the detention of 1 million Uighurs in internment camps .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"\" According to our interpreter , \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Bolton wrote ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"\" Trump said","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that Xi should go ahead with building the camps ,","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"which Trump thought","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"was exactly the right thing","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"to do. \"","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"The meeting was attended only by the two leaders and their interpreters ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"so Bolton is relying on what the interpreter told him after the meeting .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"The Uighurs , a Muslim population in China ' s Xinjiang province , have been forced into so-called \" re-education camps , \"","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"characterized by reports of torture and political indoctrination .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"A Pentagon official has described them as \" concentration camps . \"","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Beijing has imposed repressive policies on the group","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"and has Uighurs closely surveilled .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"It is a clear violation of human rights and ethnic cleansing ,","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"one","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Trump has at least condemned publicly .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"Bolton ' s book said","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"Trump opposed putting sanctions on China for the issue","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"because of trade negotiations ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"according to the Wall Street Journal .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"On Wednesday , the same day","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"as Bolton ' s book was released ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Trump signed the Uyghur Human Rights Policy Act of 2020 ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"according to the White House .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"According to Bolton ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Trump was apparently surprised","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"that the United Kingdom","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"- one of America ' s closest allies -","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"had nuclear weapons","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"during a meeting with former British Prime Minister Theresa May in 2018 .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"\" Oh , are you a nuclear power ? \"","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"according to Bolton .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"The UK was the third country","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"to acquire the nuclear bomb ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"following the US and the Soviet Union .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"It conducted its first successful test of an atomic bomb in 1952 .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Bolton writes","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"that Trump once asked his then-Chief of Staff Gen. John Kelly","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"if Finland was part of Russia .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Maybe this is more forgivable","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"when you consider","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Bolton also claims","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"that at an August 2018 White House meeting , Trump \" asserted","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"that Venezuela was ' really part of the United States '","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"and requested military options","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"to invade the South American country","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"and keep it under U.S. control , \"","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"the Wall Street Journal writes .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Trump also apparently said","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"invading Venezuela would be \" cool , \"","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"according to the Washington Post ' s account of Bolton ' s book .","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"Trump wanted to withdraw from NATO with a dramatic made-for-TV scene","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"Bolton claims","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"that during a NATO summit in 2018 , Trump decided","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"he had had enough with the historic alliance","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"and wanted out :","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"\" We will walk out ,","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"and not defend those","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"who have not [ paid ] , \"","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"read a message","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"Trump dictated to Bolton .","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"Bolton tried to stop Trump from delivering the threat ,","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"and became even more alarmed","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"when Trump told him ,","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"\" Do you want to do something historic ? \"","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"Bolton claims in the book","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"that Trump told China ' s Xi","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"that Americans wanted him to get rid of the two-term limit","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"imposed on presidents by the US Constitution .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"Bolton also claims","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"that Trump ,","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"apparently mad about leaks to the media","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"coming from inside his administration ,","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"complained in 2019","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"that journalists should be jailed .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"Bolton says","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"Trump said :","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"\" These people should be executed .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"They are scumbags . \"","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"Bolton ' s book ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"according to excerpts ,","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"also confirmed","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"that the former national security adviser saw the military aid to Ukraine as tied to investigations","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"involving Hunter Biden , former vice president Joe Biden ' s son , and Hillary Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"Per the Times :","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"On Aug. 20 , Mr. Bolton writes ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"Mr. Trump \" said","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"he wasn ' t in favor of sending them anything","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"until all the Russia-investigation materials","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"related to Clinton and Biden","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"had been turned over. \"","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"Mr. Bolton writes","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"that he , Mr. Pompeo and Defense Secretary Mark T. Esper tried eight to 10 times to get Mr. Trump to release the aid .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"Bolton also claimed","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"that Trump was fine meddling in US law enforcement","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"if it meant helping out his buddy , Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan .","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"Per the Washington Post :","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"\" Trump then told Erdogan","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"he would take care of things ,","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"explaining","depth":14},{"id":184,"text":"that the Southern District prosecutors were not his people ,","depth":16},{"id":185,"text":"but were Obama people , a problem","depth":16},{"id":186,"text":"that would be fixed","depth":16},{"id":187,"text":"when they were replaced by his people , \"","depth":16},{"id":188,"text":"Bolton writes .","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"Bolton says","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"he warned Attorney General Bill Barr about Trump ' s behavior at a meeting ,","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"where Barr expressed concerns about the \" appearances \" of Trump ' s behavior ,","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"according to the Post .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"Bolton , too , says","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"that the House ,","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"by just focusing on Ukraine ,","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"committed \" impeachment malpractice , \"","depth":13},{"id":197,"text":"because","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"if they focused elsewhere ,","depth":14},{"id":199,"text":"Bolton claims","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"\" there might have been a greater chance","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"to persuade others","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"that ' high crimes and misdemeanors ' had been perpetrated . \"","depth":15},{"id":203,"text":"If only there were someone","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"who could have changed that .","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"Every day at , we aim to answer your most important questions","depth":4},{"id":206,"text":"and provide you , and our audience around the world , with information","depth":5},{"id":207,"text":"that has the power","depth":6},{"id":208,"text":"to save lives .","depth":6},{"id":209,"text":"Our mission has never been more vital","depth":6},{"id":210,"text":"than it is in this moment :","depth":6},{"id":211,"text":"to empower you","depth":6},{"id":212,"text":"through understanding .","depth":6},{"id":213,"text":"' s work is reaching more people than ever ,","depth":6},{"id":214,"text":"but our distinctive brand of explanatory journalism takes resources","depth":7},{"id":215,"text":"- particularly during a pandemic and an economic downturn .","depth":7},{"id":216,"text":"Your financial contribution will not constitute a donation ,","depth":7},{"id":217,"text":"but it will enable our staff to continue to offer free articles , videos , and podcasts at the quality and volume","depth":8},{"id":218,"text":"that this moment requires .","depth":8},{"id":219,"text":"Please consider making a contribution to today .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":439,"left